# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .cfignore — Cloud Foundry upload exclusions for a2a-client-service
#
# Build strategy: compile TypeScript locally BEFORE running `cf push`.
#
#   npm run build   # tsc → produces dist/ with correct ESM output
#   cf push         # uploads dist/ + package.json + package-lock.json
#
# The Node.js buildpack then runs `npm ci --production` to install only the
# runtime dependencies (no devDeps needed — compiled JS is already present).
#
# Uploaded to CF (minimal set):
#   dist/            compiled ESM JavaScript — the only runtime artefact
#   package.json     runtime dependency manifest
#   package-lock.json  lockfile for reproducible npm ci
#   manifest.yaml    CF deployment descriptor
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Dependencies ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rebuilt by the Node.js buildpack; uploading them wastes quota and bandwidth.
node_modules/

# ── TypeScript source & tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only the compiled output in dist/ is needed at runtime.
# IMPORTANT: always run `npm run build` before `cf push` to regenerate dist/.
# TypeScript with "module": "Node16" + "type": "module" in package.json emits
# correct ESM; a stale CJS dist/ (built before "type":"module" was added)
# causes "exports is not defined in ES module scope" at startup.
src/
tsconfig.json
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Local / development configuration ────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER upload local credentials or environment overrides to CF.
.env
default-env.json
.env.example

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# ── Documentation ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
README.md

# ── Version control ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore

# ── Editor & IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── OS artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
